entries.femaleVariant: Hm. Think you'd better stock up. Heard some of the sellers here are askin' for trouble.
Startin' to be late on their "rent."
Hm, no shortage o' scopsuckers, is there…?
Ey, wait. Maybe they'll knock the prices down a bit? Since they're in deep shit already?
Yeeeah! Now you're usin' that skullsponge.
Tygers could show up at any second, turn this place upside down – there goes all our biz.
